properties.title: Bi-Variate Map of Wildfires in California
properties.info: This bivariate map represents wildfires in California from 2009-2019. The symbol size represents size in acres >= 100 and the colors represent the five most common cause of fire during this time period. The data came from the U.S. Forest Service; FIRESTAT Fire Occurrence - Yearly Update.
